<DATE>10/03/2009</DATE>
<AUTHOR>Bmore Fuzz</AUTHOR>
<TEXT>Traded my 2006 Ridgeline RT for the 2009 RTL. This truck was so practical and reliable in the past 3.5 years I decided to do it all over again...this time with the leather, Navigation, XM radio and sunroof. The 2006 I traded in with 60K miles drove as good as the day I drove it home new. The 2009 feels a bit tighter and quieter but considering the 2006 was its 1st year production, Honda just kept improving it and it shows!</TEXT>
<FAVORITE>Full size trunk in bed and bulletproof reliability. RTL is Honda's answer to the Escalade pickup!</FAVORITE>
